                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6842" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0685</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7760 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中旅香格里拉：创新催开沪滇对口帮扶项目之花</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CTG Diqing Shangri-La Tourism Investment and Development Company Limited: Innovation promotes the blossoming of shanghai-Yunnan paired poverty alleviation projects</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">倪向丽，周广宇，王林璟，赵冬梅，唐琴</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国旅游集团迪庆香格里拉旅游投资发展有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">管理创新；旅游扶贫模式；委托运营管理；企业社会责任；乡村振兴；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Management innovation; Tourism poverty alleviation model; Entrusted operation management; Corporate social responsibility; Rural revitalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了中国旅游集团香格里拉公司在新冠肺炎疫情冲击旅游市场、自身经营陷于困境的情况下，面临是否承接沪滇帮扶旅游扶贫项目的决策难题。在多方权衡后，公司决定克服自身困难，发扬央企担当，承接项目建设。通过创造性的“运营管理参与旅游扶贫”模式，公司有效控制了参与帮扶项目带来的经营风险，充分发挥自身优势，成功推进旅游扶贫项目落地云南香格里拉，为该地区打造了可持续“造血”产业，以实际行动助力乡村振兴。通过案例研习，引导学生深入思考管理创新的内涵和内容，帮助学生深刻认识创新之于企业履责和创造价值的重要意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the difficult decision of Shangri-La, a Chinese tourism group, whether to undertake the Shanghai-Yunnan tourism poverty alleviation project or not, under the circumstances of the impact of the COVID-19 epidemic on the tourism market and the difficulties in its own operation. After weighing various aspects, the company decided to overcome its own difficulties, carry forward the central enterprise responsibility, and undertake project construction. Through the creative mode of &quot;operation management and participation in tourism poverty alleviation&quot;, the company effectively controlled the business risks caused by participating in the assistance project, gave full play to its own advantages, and successfully promoted the implementation of the tourism poverty alleviation project in Shangri-La, Yunnan, creating a sustainable &quot;hematopoietic&quot; industry for the region, and helping rural revitalization with practical actions. Through case study, students are guided to think deeply about the connotation and content of management innovation, and to help students have a deep understanding of the significance of innovation in corporate responsibility and value creation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新创业管理》、《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风险控制理论；企业社会责任理论；管理创新理论；公司社会创业运营模式；委托运营管理；旅游扶贫模式；利益联结机制；创新理论；可持续发展理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-11</td>
                            </tr>
